</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think this book would be appropriate for a mature 12 year old. There is a quite a bit of violence-beheading, people burned, eaten by creatures etc. <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">â€¦more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think this book would be appropriate for a mature 12 year old. There is a quite a bit of violence-beheading, people burned, eaten by creatures etc. So if I were a parent I would look through before giving it to my kid. But if you are the 'kid' in question I would really say it's about the amount of violence you are comfortable with. The book's really good though! ;) <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
