<div id="review_1820968091" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1820968091" />
    <a title="Abby" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/56868213-abby"><img alt="Abby" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1623558258p2/56868213.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1820968091?book_show_action=true">Feb 09, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Abby" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Abby" href="/user/show/56868213-abby">Abby</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56868213-abby?shelf=books-i-own">books-i-own</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56868213-abby?shelf=middle-grade">middle-grade</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56868213-abby?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56868213-abby?shelf=christian-fiction">christian-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56868213-abby?shelf=2021-february-reading">2021-february-reading</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1820968091" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3860850724955702651">1) The last five chapters of this had me legitimately stressed because I couldn&apos;t remember who makes it out, lol<br/>2) Sir Aelic was one of my first book boyfriends and I had forgotten that fact until now <br/>3) Yes I will be diving into The Final Storm immediately and yes I&apos;m very much looking forward to it.</span>
